      <title>IntelliJ IDEA Tomcat Configuration</title>
      <link href="/2022/01/17/tomcatconfig/"/>
      <url>/2022/01/17/tomcatconfig/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="English-version-steps"><a href="#English-version-steps" class="headerlink" title="English version steps"></a>English version steps</h1><ol><li>Open IDEA</li></ol><hr><ol start="2"><li>Click on the “Edit configuration” option of the current project<br><img src="P1-1.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="3"><li>In the upper left corner “+” find the “Tomcat Server” option, select “local” (local can only be accessed by yourself)<br><img src="P1-2.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="4"><li>Configure “Name” at the top right<br><img src="P1-3.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="5"><li>Application server configuration.<ol><li><a href="https://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi">https://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi</a>, download the zip from the official website, unzip it to an empty folder of your choice</li><li>Back to IDEA, select the path of apache.tomcat folder you just extracted.<br><img src="P1-4.png"></li></ol></li></ol><hr><ol start="6"><li>uncheck “After launch” (optional), JRE select 1.8 (for me will be an error, or the default on the line, mine is 16), port: “HTTP port 8080”, JMX. “port 1099”<br><img src="P1-5.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="7"><li>Click on “Deployment” in the bar above, select “Artifact” from the “+” on the right, then make sure your project ends with this “-web:war exploded” (must end in exploded) click OK, then pull down to “Application context” and change the name: remove the “_war_exploaded” delete (optional, here for convenience), and then click OK.<br><img src="P1-6-1.png"><br><img src="P1-6-2.png"><br><img src="P1-6-3.png"></li></ol><hr><ul><li>If you visit the port <a href="http://localhost:8080/YourProjectName_war_exploded/">http://localhost:8080/YourProjectName_war_exploded/</a><ul><li>where “/YourProjectName_war_exploded/ “ (after “<a href="http://localhost:8080&quot;">http://localhost:8080"</a>)<br>You can find it in the “application context” in the “deployment” section of the tomcat configuration</li></ul></li></ul><hr><h1 id="中文版本步骤"><a href="#中文版本步骤" class="headerlink" title="中文版本步骤"></a>中文版本步骤</h1><p>Tomcat 配置</p><ol><li>打开IDEA</li></ol><hr><ol start="2"><li>点击当前项目的“Edit configuration”选项<br><img src="P1-1.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="3"><li>在左上角“+”号 找到“Tomcat Server”选项，选取“local”即可（local只能自己访问）<br><img src="P1-2.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="4"><li>右侧上方配置“Name”<br><img src="P1-3.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="5"><li>Application server的配置：<ol><li><a href="https://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi">https://tomcat.apache.org/download-90.cgi</a><br>官网下载zip，解压到你自己选取的一个空文件夹</li><li>回到IDEA，选取你刚解压缩后apache.tomcat文件夹的路径。<br><img src="P1-4.png"></li></ol></li></ol><hr><ol start="6"><li>取消勾选“After launch”（可选），JRE选取1.8(对我而言会出错，或者默认就行了，我的是16)，端口：“HTTP port 8080”，JMX：“port 1099”<br><img src="P1-5.png"></li></ol><hr><ol start="7"><li>上方bar中点击“Deployment”，右边“+”选取“Artifact”，然后确保你的项目以这个结尾“-web:war exploded”（必须是exploded结尾）点击OK，然后拉到下面“Application context”改个名字：把后面的“_war_exploaded”删除（可选，这里为了方便），然后点击OK即可<br><img src="P1-6-1.png"><br><img src="P1-6-2.png"><br><img src="P1-6-3.png"></li></ol><hr><ul><li>访问的话 端口 <a href="http://localhost:8080/YourProjectName_war_exploded/%E3%80%82">http://localhost:8080/YourProjectName_war_exploded/。</a><ul><li>其中 “/YourProjectName_war_exploded/ ” （在“<a href="http://localhost:8080”后面）">http://localhost:8080”后面）</a><br>在配置tomcat地方“deployment”的“application context“中可以找到 </li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
